forkee.name: medimate
forkee.description: Android app made using Flutter, Firebase, and Google Cloud Vision. MediMate allows users to scan medication labels with their phones, which will then generate dosage reminders, alert users of potential side-effects & dangerous medication combinations, and update a user medical profile.
